2x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/chad-cky@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/cky">CKY</a>主唱查德·金斯伯格 (Chad I Ginsburg) 声称，出于自卫，他打了<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/alien-ant-farm">外星蚂蚁农场 (Alien Ant Farm)</a>的德莱顿·米切尔 (Dryden Mitchell) 的脸 - 看看金斯伯格在下面怎么说。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-interviews/primal-scream-bobby-gillespie-interview-come-ahead-3810374">原始尖叫在他们的抗议迪斯科专辑中：“如果你要从屋顶尖叫，没有比这更好的时机了”</a></strong></li></ul><p>上周末（11 月 9 日），Alien Ant Farm 和 CKY 拉开了联合巡演英国站的序幕， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/alien-ant-farm-cky-joint-uk-tour-with-1-ticket-levy-for-grassroots-venues-buy-tickets-3752024">该巡演早在 4 月份就已宣布</a>。然而，就在马盖特梦幻世界开幕前几个小时，外星人蚂蚁农场的德莱顿·米切尔<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/alien-ant-farms-dryden-mitchell-kicks-cky-off-tour-after-frontman-chad-i-ginsburg-punches-him-in-the-face-3811273">宣布 CKY 被取消巡演</a>。</p><p>当时，米切尔解释说，他曾质问金斯伯格，称他“在欧洲演出中对待多名工作人员和开场乐队成员就像垃圾一样，并在我们的营地引起了普遍的戏剧性事件”，然后他被打了一拳。 </p><figure id="attachment_3811438" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3811438" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3811438" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/cky-chad-ginsburg@2000x1270.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/cky-chad-ginsburg@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/cky-chad-ginsburg@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/cky-chad-ginsburg@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/cky-chad-ginsburg@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/cky-chad-ginsburg@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/cky-chad-ginsburg@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3811438" class="wp-caption-text"> CKY 的查德·金斯伯格。图片来源：克里斯蒂·古德温/盖蒂图片社</figcaption></figure><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/cky-frontman-says-he-had-no-choice-and-good-reason-for-punching-alien-ant-farms-dryden-mitchell-in-the-face-3811437">本周早些时候，金斯伯格简短地解释道</a>：“英国 CKY 粉丝可以拿回你们的钱！！！对于所发生的事情，我别无选择，也没有充分的理由。我将永远捍卫自己。你比我更了解我！”</p><p>然而现在，这位 CKY 主唱扩展了他的主张，在 Instagram 的一篇 <a href="https://consequence.net/2024/11/cky-frontman-defends-punching-alien-ant-farm-singer/"><em>故事</em></a>中写道：“保护自己免受坏人的伤害并没有错。如果你受到攻击或感到真正受到威胁，请不要害怕并尽你所能阻止威胁。”</p><p>金斯伯格继续说道：“我必须保护自己。这是对一个非常愤怒的家伙的瞬间反应，他嘀咕着然后大喊#*%！从 10 英尺外冲向我，进入我的个人空间！向我而来。他在攻击我！我感受到了身体上的威胁，如果我没有试图避免攻击，我就会受到攻击。为了他妈的缘故。” </p><figure id="attachment_3811440" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3811440" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3811440" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/chad-ginsburg-cky@2000x1270.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/chad-ginsburg-cky@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/chad-ginsburg-cky@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/chad-ginsburg-cky@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/chad-ginsburg-cky@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/chad-ginsburg-cky@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/chad-ginsburg-cky@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3811440" class="wp-caption-text"> CKY 的查德·金斯伯格。图片来源：Kevin Nixon/Classic Rock Magazine/Future Publishing via Getty Images</figcaption></figure><p>剩余的外星蚂蚁农场日期将按计划进行 - 您可以<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/alien-ant-farm-cky-joint-uk-tour-with-1-ticket-levy-for-grassroots-venues-buy-tickets-3752024">在此处</a>查看完整的日期列表，并且可以<a href="https://ticketmaster-u